  "page": "Daeron",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Daeron</b> can refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Targaryen_(son_of_Viserys_I)\" title=\"Daeron Targaryen (son of Viserys I)\">Daeron Targaryen</a>, youngest son of King Viserys I Targaryen and Queen Alicent Hightower, also called <i>the Daring</i></li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron I Targaryen\">Daeron I Targaryen</a>, son of King Aegon III Targaryen and Queen Daenaera Velaryon, also called <i>the Young Dragon</i></li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>, son of Aegon IV Targaryen and Queen Naerys Targaryen, also called <i>the Good</i></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Daeron Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Daeron Targaryen</a>, eldest son of King Maekar I Targaryen and Lady Dyanna Dayne, also called <i>the Drunken</i></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Targaryen_(son_of_Aegon_V)\" title=\"Daeron Targaryen (son of Aegon V)\">Daeron Targaryen</a>, youngest son of King Aegon V Targaryen and Queen Betha Blackwood</li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Targaryen_(son_of_Aerys_II)\" title=\"Daeron Targaryen (son of Aerys II)\">Daeron Targaryen</a>, son of King Aerys II Targaryen and Queen Rhaella Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Vaith\" title=\"Daeron Vaith\">Daeron Vaith</a>, Lord of the Red Dunes</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_Velaryon\" title=\"Daeron Velaryon\">Daeron Velaryon</a>, father of Queen Daenaera Velaryon</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daeron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h